# Real-Time Presence & Activity API Endpoints

This document describes the backend API endpoints for the Real-Time Presence & Activity System.

## Presence API Endpoints

### POST /api/presence/update
Update user's presence status.

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "userId": "uuid",
  "status": "online" | "away" | "busy" | "offline",
  "location": {
    "type": "page" | "event",
    "id": "string"
  }
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "presence": {
    "user_id": "uuid",
    "status": "online",
    "location_type": "page",
    "location_id": "dashboard",
    "last_seen": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

**Requirements:** 1.1, 1.2, 2.4

---

